The paper deals with autonomous exploration using aerial vehicles, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of collisions as a means of navigation involves processing sensor data, which can be related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The reactive planner and control law mentioned in the paper can be considered as a control system, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper involves developing algorithms for state estimation, which can be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
